      "content": "small reasons to hold on... i don't know. it sounds like you're just describing a way to prolong the pain. every little thing i do just feels like a performance for an audience that isn't there anymore. it's not just sadness, it's like the world has lost its color. it feels more like i'm just a ghost haunting my own life. what's the point of trying to \"hold on\" to a life that doesn't even feel like mine anymore?",
